        "description": "在固定床反应器中使用不同结晶度的Y沸石催化剂（以及MIL-53(Cu)衍生物改性的Y沸石催化剂）对城市塑料废物进行催化热解，生产汽油、喷气燃料和柴油范围的燃料。反应在氮气气氛下于400°C、450°C和500°C进行。",
        "text_snippet": "Catalytic pyrolysis of municipal plastic waste over nano MIL-53 (Cu) derived @ zeolite Y for gasoline, jet fuel, and diesel range fuel production... The test results in a fixed bed reactor for every twelve samples of catalyst and their effect on the efficiency of different sections of liquid fuel show a significant improvement in the desired product.",
